{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e5136bf071","title":"中共中央政治局四月一日会议情况","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"18ea1fe946","index":0,"year":1976,"month":4,"day":2,"articleId":"e5136bf071","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"邓小平","id":"5bd9678625","type":"人物"},{"name":"中共中央决定、指示等","id":"94b82e4994","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"重要会议","id":"afdf5cd1a7","type":"主题"},{"name":"批邓反击右倾翻案风","id":"b88b47c25d","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛远新","id":"f8d6ecb146","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"aa59d172f0","type":"title","text":"中共中央政治局四月一日会议情况","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ef14de6fa","type":"paragraph","text":"主  席：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"084820a84f","type":"paragraph","text":"四月一日晚，政治局讨论了几件事：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5625e5fec0","type":"paragraph","text":"一，当前全国各地流传所谓“总理遗嘱”“总理给主席的诗词”欺骗了一些不明真象的人，干扰破坏当前反击右倾翻案风的斗争，南京已有人借故闹事，还要利用清明节（四月四日）搞什么扫墓活动，并要以纪念杨开慧烈士名义送花圈。北京等地也有很多类似东西，这个动向值得注意。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3ab478c9d9","type":"paragraph","text":"除电话答复江苏等地外，中央可以正式发一文件，说明所谓遗嘱之类，是敌人造的谣言，干扰破坏当前的斗争大方向，要追查，不要上当。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c04c721dd1","type":"paragraph","text":"二、今年五一节的活动","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1173e31409","type":"paragraph","text":"有的同志提出不搞游园活动了，应改革一下，还有见报不好安排等。讨论结果，五一节的活动今后可以改革，一年搞一次（国庆节）即可。但今年改变不利，当前国内外敌人都说我们乱了套，要钻空子，历年有活动，今年不搞影响太大。要利用这个机会体现安定、团结，庆祝反击右倾翻案风的初步胜利，鼓舞全国人民，还是按去年的办法不变。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef59cdf7ab","type":"paragraph","text":"至于登报排列，可分三个公园分别报导，不搞通栏，只登政治局同志、副委员长、副总理，不搞过去上千人的大名单。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f0dec4fbc","type":"paragraph","text":"建议邓小平同志不出席，其他政治局同志尽量都出席。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f6b28edd7","type":"paragraph","text":"三、三月初主席指示，《毛主席的重要指示》暂时就传达到县团级，暂不扩大传达。目前干部已学习了近一个月，党员、基层干部普遍要求传达，是否可以考虑下一步再扩大传达到支部书记和各级机关的党员干部。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8361a826c5","type":"paragraph","text":"上述意见当否，请主席指示。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"210ae26869","type":"paragraph","text":"如同意，国锋同志准备正式向主席写报告。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91393e3597","type":"paragraph","text":"退  毛远新","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"546fa84a19","type":"paragraph","text":"四月二日","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb925641bb","type":"paragraph","text":"注：毛泽东四月三日阅批：“同意”。此件是中央办公厅秘书局提供的。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e5136bf071","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}